    public abstract class NodeListAdapter
extends AbstractList<Node>
    Adapt a collection from the W3C DOM library to be a List compatible with the Java Collections Framework.

        public static List<Node> wrap(NodeList nodes)
        Wrap a node list. The returned list is an unmodifiable view and supports all non-destructive operations. Any changes in the underlying list will be reflected in this object.

        Returns:
